These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, british
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, sailing
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, bike
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the british is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | british    | argentine |
| Sport         | sailing | soccer    |
| Transport     | jet-ski     | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, russian
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the brazilian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | cola  | soy-milk   |
| Nationality   | russian | brazilian  |
| Transport     | snowmobile   | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, dancing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, drama
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, baseball
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
2. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | woodworking   | dancing  |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | musical  |
| Sport         | tennis   | baseball |

 #################################

 
