.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: lime, pumpkin
The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, freelancer
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, climbing
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the software-developer##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
3. the person eating lime is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pumpkin | lime     |
| Job     | freelancer | software-developer |
| Sport   | climbing | rowing    |

 #################################

 
