.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-14::.
There 2 different types of food: watermelon, pear
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, filmmaking
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | pear | watermelon  |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | hiking |
| Pet     | chinchilla  | mouse     |

