.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, magic-tricks
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, turkish
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the thai is on the left of the turkish##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | camping |
| Nationality   | thai     | turkish     |
| Pet           | fish          | goldfish     |

